name: Paul Di'Anno
summary: Paul Di'Anno, the original lead vocalist of iconic heavy metal band Iron Maiden, has passed away at the age of 66. Di'Anno's tenure with Iron Maiden spanned their early years and included contributions to the band's first two studio albums, "Iron Maiden" and "Killers." As news of his passing spreads, tributes and condolences pour in from the music world and fans alike, honoring the legacy he leaves behind as a founding member of one of the most influential heavy metal bands of all time.

name: Fethullah Gülen
summary: Fethullah Gülen, a Turkish spiritual leader and former close ally of President Recep Tayyip Erdoğan, has passed away in Pennsylvania. Gülen was accused by the Turkish government of orchestrating a failed coup attempt in 2016, leading to his exile in the US. He was widely considered a powerful cleric and a prominent figure in Turkish politics. His death marks the end of a long and controversial chapter in Turkey's history, characterized by his rivalry with Erdoğan and the subsequent crackdown on his followers. Gülen's legacy will likely continue to be debated in Turkish society, as it has been a source of political and social division for many years.

She also revealed that she immediately called Applegate after her diagnosis and that one celebrity had an unexpected "salty" reaction. The interviews provide insights into her experiences with cancer and highlight the importance of support and resilience during such challenging times.

summary: In a highly anticipated matchup on Sunday Night Football, the Pittsburgh Steelers defeated the New York Jets 37-15. Despite an early lead, the Jets succumbed to a second-half collapse, with Russell Wilson's debut for the Steelers proving to be a catalyst. The loss marks a significant setback for the Jets, who had hoped to build on their Week 6 victory over the Buffalo Bills. Experts and analysts had predicted a competitive game, but the Steelers ultimately dominated, raising questions about the Jets' resilience and potential. The acquisition of wide receiver Davante Adams by the Jets has also generated buzz, as they seek to strengthen their offense for future games.

summary: The New York Mets are facing elimination in the National League Championship Series (NLCS) after losing Game 5 to the Los Angeles Dodgers. summary: The New York Mets' NLCS run has come to an end, as they fell to the Los Angeles Dodgers in Game 6. The Mets had a disappointing Game 3 at home, but they showed resilience in Game 5, saving their season with a big win. However, the Dodgers dominated Game 6, seizing control of the series and sending the Mets home. The Mets' bullpen played a crucial role in extending their NLCS hopes, but it wasn't enough to overcome the Dodgers' strong performance. The series now shifts back to California, with the Dodgers on the cusp of victory and the Mets trying to keep their magic alive. Despite the disappointing end, it was an amazing season for the Mets, especially for one fan's son, who enjoyed the incredible run.
